        "description": "Used to get more specific results when using \"Interest by region\" data type. Other data types do not accept this parameter. The default value depends on the geo location that is set. Available options: - `country`: Country - `region`: Subregion - `dma`: Metro - `city`: City Note: Not all region options will return results for every geo location.",
